<html>
    <head>
        <title>New Vendor Alert</title>
    </head>
    <body style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;'>
        <div style='max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 20px;'>
            <header style='text-align: center;'>
                <h1 style='color: #f59e0b;'>Terminus ALERT: New Vendor</h1>
            </header>
            <section>
                <p>Hello Admin,</p>
                <p>A new vendor has just registered on the platform and is waiting for onboarding/KYC verification.</p>
                <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
                <p><strong>Vendor Name:</strong> {{vendorName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{vendorEmail}}</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{vendorPhone}}</p>
                <p><strong>Market Category:</strong> {{marketCategory}}</p>
                <p><strong>Signup Date:</strong> {{signupDate}}</p>
                <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
                <p>Please log in to the admin dashboard to review their application and verify their business documents.</p>
            </section>
            <footer style='text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;'>
                <p style='color: #aaa;'>&copy; 2026 Terminus Drive Limited</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
